Hello, thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers! My name is Kenneth Cooper. May I ask who I'm speaking with today?

Hi Kenneth, this is Catherine Garcia.

Thank you, Catherine. How can I assist you today?

I'm having some issues with the navigation equipment on my yacht. I was hoping you could help me out.

Of course, Catherine! Can you please describe the malfunction you're experiencing?

Yes, the GPS seems to be inaccurate, and it's causing some concern during my trips.

I understand. To proceed, could I have the model number of your equipment, please?

It's model number eight seven six five.

Thank you, and for verification purposes, could you also provide your berth number?

Sure, it's one zero three at the Marina Bay.

Great, Catherine. Let me check on that for you. We will do our best to resolve the issue swiftly. Thank you for your patience and for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a wonderful day!
